&lt;p&gt;I cam to &lt;a data-goodreads-type=&#34;book&#34; data-goodreads-id=&#34;33080122&#34; href=&#34;https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/33080122.the-calculating-stars&#34;&gt; The Calculating Stars &lt;/a&gt; by way of the &lt;a href=&#34;https://writingexcuses.com/&#34;&gt; Writing Excuses &lt;/a&gt; podcast. I&amp;rsquo;ve read all of &lt;a data-goodreads-type=&#34;author&#34; data-goodreads-id=&#34;38550&#34; href=&#34;https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/38550.brandon-sanderson&#34;&gt; Brandon Sanderson &lt;/a&gt; , most of &lt;a data-goodreads-type=&#34;author&#34; data-goodreads-id=&#34;516182&#34; href=&#34;https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/516182.howard-tayler&#34;&gt; Howard Tayler &lt;/a&gt; &amp;rsquo;s [ Schlock Mercenary ](&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.goodreads.com/series/50869-schlock-&#34;&gt;https://www.goodreads.com/series/50869-schlock-&lt;/a&gt; mercenary) series, and &lt;a data-goodreads-type=&#34;author&#34; data-goodreads-id=&#34;2740668&#34; href=&#34;https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/2740668.dan-wells&#34;&gt; Dan Wells &lt;/a&gt; &amp;rsquo;s &lt;a data-goodreads-type=&#34;book&#34; data-goodreads-id=&#34;12476820&#34; href=&#34;https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/12476820.partials&#34;&gt; Partials &lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a data-goodreads-type=&#34;book&#34; data-goodreads-id=&#34;35120549&#34; href=&#34;https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/35120549.i-am-not-a-serial-killer&#34;&gt; I Am Not a Serial Killer &lt;/a&gt; series and loved them all. The one outstanding author? &lt;a data-goodreads-type=&#34;author&#34; data-goodreads-id=&#34;2868678&#34; href=&#34;https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/2868678.mary-robinette-kowal&#34;&gt; Mary Robinette Kowal &lt;/a&gt; .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I was not at all disappointed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
